      <title>特朗普亲属在 X 上发布虚假加密货币公告遭黑客攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-relatives-are-hacked-on-x-with-fake-crypto-announcement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，一些特朗普家族成员的社交媒体资料遭到入侵，用于发布有关加密项目的虚假公告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-relatives-are-hacked-on-x-with-fake-crypto-announcement</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:02:09 GMT</pubDate>
