    <item>
      <title>马科斯誓言在逮捕陷入困境的前市长后迅速伸张正义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ex-philippine-mayor-tied-to-laundering-nabbed-in-indonesia-abs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统费迪南德·马科斯 (Ferdinand Marcos Jr.) 誓言要迅速解决针对一名前市长的洗钱和人口贩卖指控的案件。周三，该市长在印度尼西亚被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ex-philippine-mayor-tied-to-laundering-nabbed-in-indonesia-abs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 00:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普未能将纽约封口费案移交联邦法院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-loses-bid-to-move-ny-hush-money-case-to-federal-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国法官裁定，前总统唐纳德·特朗普不能将其在纽约的封口费案转交给联邦法院，此举可能会导致其原定于 9 月 18 日的宣判被推迟到 11 月总统大选之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-loses-bid-to-move-ny-hush-money-case-to-federal-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基阴谋变阵 六名乌克兰部长提出辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/three-ukrainian-ministers-resign-in-broader-cabinet-shuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库列巴于周三提交辞呈，在外界猜测乌克兰政府准备进行大规模改组之际，两天内内阁部长总数增至六名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/three-ukrainian-ministers-resign-in-broader-cabinet-shuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:54:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
